questions.question: A person is holding an object o1; later on, the person is drinking from o1 while being inside of it.
questions.dsl: holding(o0, o1); (drinking_from(o0, o1), in(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person'))

questions.question: A person is initially behind and touching an object o1. Later, the person is located beneath the same object o1.
A person o0 is inside an object o1. Subsequently, the person is beneath the same object and is wearing it.
A person o0 is initially behind and drinking from an object o1. Later, the person is inside the object o1.
Initially, an object o0 is holding another object o1 and o0 is inside o1. Later, the same object o0, which is a person, is drinking from o1.
A person is beneath another object o1 and is eating from o1. Later, the person is in front of o1.
questions.dsl: (beneath(o0, o1), eating(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person')); in_front_of(o0, o1)

questions.question: Initially, a person is in front of another object o1. Following this, the person is inside of o1 and is sitting on o1.
questions.dsl: in_front_of(o0, o1); (in(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person'), sitting_on(o0, o1))

questions.question: A person is in front of an object o1. Later, the person moves to be behind o1 and is carrying o1.
A person is behind an object o1, and later on, the same person is beneath o1 and is touching o1.
A person is above and behind another object o1 and is sitting on o1.
questions.dsl: (above(o0, o1), behind(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person'), sitting_on(o0, o1))
